#: ../../Y/YAUN.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Acronym for ‘Yet Another Unix Nerd’] Reported from the San Diego Computer "
"Society (predominantly a microcomputer users' group) as a good-natured "
"punning insult aimed at Unix zealots."
msgstr ""
"[‘Yet Another Unix Nerd’(またしてもUnixオタク)の頭字語] San Diego Computer "
"Society(主にマイクロコンピュータユーザのグループ)から報告された、Unix信奉者に向けられた善意ある語呂合わせの侮辱。"
